        public void use(org.bukkit.event.player.PlayerInteractEvent event)

      • taunt

        public static void taunt(org.bukkit.entity.Player player)
        Creates a 10 block wide particle circle around the player and taunts every entity inside of it, forcing it to attack the player. Makes the shield loose 3 durability.
        Parameters:
        player - The player that is taunting the entities.
        See Also:
        Cooldown.playerWeaponSkillUse(Player, String), ParticleSpawner.spawnParticleCircle(Location, SkillParticle, double, int), DurabilityCalculator.damageItem(Player, org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack, int, boolean)

      • addPattern

        public static void addPattern(org.bukkit.inventory.meta.ItemMeta shieldItemMeta)
        Adds a random pattern to the given shield item meta. It will receive either black or white as base and a colorful emblem as first pattern layer.
        Parameters:
        shieldItemMeta - The item meta of a shield.
